revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yakubovs}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yakubov'' is the 25924<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 948 individuals.
